trans-unit.source: A static extension methods class for getting either an <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> or <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> instance from a <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Uma classe de métodos de extensão estática para obter uma instância de <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> ou de <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> de uma instância de <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" /> instance from which to get the <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: A instância de <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" /> da qual obter a instância de <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" />.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> instance from an <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma instância de <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> de uma instância de <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" /> instance from which to get the <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: A instância de <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" /> da qual obter a instância de <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" />.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> instance from an <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma instância de <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> de uma instância de <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message" />.
